  "title": "👥 Team Growth Executive (Sales & Marketing)",
  "description": "<p>👥 <strong>Team Growth Executive (Sales & Marketing)</strong><br /><strong>Sales-Focused | Travel Opportunities | Leadership Development</strong></p><p>Support campaign execution while learning how to recruit, train, and lead a team. A great starting point for future leaders.</p><p>This role is designed for <strong>young, ambitious individuals</strong> who want more than just a job. You’ll start by executing <strong>face-to-face sales and marketing campaigns</strong>, while being trained in team growth, leadership, and people development. High performers will progress into <strong>team leader and management roles</strong>, with opportunities to travel as part of campaign expansion.</p><p>This is a <strong>hands-on, performance-driven role</strong>, not a desk-based or digital-only position.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Execute <strong>on-ground sales and marketing campaigns</strong></p></li><li><p>Represent client brands through direct customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Support campaign expansion and performance tracking</p></li><li><p>Learn how to <strong>recruit, train, and develop sales teams</strong></p></li><li><p>Coach and support new team members</p></li><li><p>Travel for campaign execution, team support, and growth opportunities</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Provide</strong></h3><p>✈️ Local & regional <strong>travel opportunities</strong><br />📚 Structured sales & leadership training<br />🤝 Ongoing mentorship from experienced leaders<br />💰 Performance-based earnings (commission structure)<br />📈 Clear pathway into team leadership and management<br />🌱 Personal development in confidence, communication, and leadership<br />🔥 Young, driven, and ambitious team culture</p><h3><strong>Who This Role Is For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Young, ambitious candidates ready to grow fast</p></li><li><p>Fresh graduates / ORD personnel / career switchers</p></li><li><p>Individuals who enjoy <strong>sales, people interaction, and travel</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong learning attitude with leadership aspirations</p></li><li><p>Comfortable stepping outside their comfort zone</p></li></ul><p>⚠️ <strong>Important:</strong><br />This role involves <strong>direct sales and face-to-face marketing execution</strong>, including travel for campaigns.<br />It is <strong>not</strong> a digital marketing or office-only role.</p><p>👉 <strong>Apply now</strong> if you’re looking to build sales skills, leadership experience, and a career with real growth and travel opportunities.</p>",
